snippet: The former Swedish prince, whom the Grand Duchess of Luxembourg made a count five years after he wed Kerstin Wijkmark, became a businessman in Manhattan.
abstract: Carl Johan Bernadotte, Swedish prince who renounced his title to marry a commoner and later became a businessman in Manhattan, dies at age 95.
lead_paragraph: The former Swedish prince, whom the Grand Duchess of Luxembourg made a count five years after he wed Kerstin Wijkmark, became a businessman in Manhattan.

headline.seo: Carl Johan Bernadotte, 95, Swedish Prince Who Followed Love, Dies
headline.main: Carl Bernadotte, Prince Whose First Loyalty Was Love, Dies at 95
headline.print_headline: Carl Bernadotte, 95, a Prince Whose First Loyalty Was Love
